name: A Few Programming Projects and Snippets
body:
### Starting something new
I'm relatively new to GitHub, but I've been programming off and on for a while now. I study electrical engineering, so the bulk of my programming is modeling and data processing scripts. Most of what you see here won't be much more than snippets of code, but I have the occasional, more ambitious project. If you don't see my work here yet, you can always find it on my regular GitHub profile.
